<item>
            <title>[LU-10973] LNet Unit Test Framework (LUTF) Autotest Integration</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10973</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The LUTF is a tool that can functionally test LNet through exercising its DLC interface. It&apos;s a python based tool that currently has a repository of 95 scripts and growing that test the DLC feature and the MR feature.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This ticket is opened to determine the best approach to integrate this tool in AT.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For more details on the design and usage of the LUTF please refer to:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.whamcloud.com/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=36973031&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://wiki.whamcloud.com/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=36973031&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
